From: Srinivas Pandruvada <srinivas.pandruvada@linux.intel.com>
Date: Tue, 29 Apr 2014 09:51:29 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Deny non root users to send system bus dbus messages

Change the default policy to deny non root users.
---
 data/org.freedesktop.thermald.conf | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/data/org.freedesktop.thermald.conf b/data/org.freedesktop.thermald.conf
index ff65452..41aa8d0 100644
--- a/data/org.freedesktop.thermald.conf
+++ b/data/org.freedesktop.thermald.conf
@@ -20,7 +20,7 @@
         </policy>
 
         <policy context="default">
-                <allow send_destination="org.freedesktop.thermald"/>
+                <deny send_destination="org.freedesktop.thermald"/>
                 <allow receive_sender="org.freedesktop.thermald"/>
         </policy>
 
